/lih.kg/1219585</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n你好，<br />\n作為香港既KOL, 係應該做Key Opinion Leader應該做既事！<br />\n如果你是支持這次香港的抗爭運動，希望你能夠發揮不同角色的作用，係你既網絡平台上發聲！<br />\n<br />\n作歌既可以作歌，拍片既可以拍片，寫文既可以寫文。<br />\n但絕對唔係求其出個story, 影下地下，影下天空，就話自己緊張香港。<br />\n<br />\n亦希望你清楚表明自己的立場，不是食大茶飯講d唔講d, 而係真真正正講出你對引渡法既睇法！<br />\n<br />\n當你口說支持，但又沒有就著KOL的角色，在網絡平台沒有就香港的抗爭作出清晰的回應和表明立場，身為Key Opinion Leader, 你慚愧嗎？"},{"pid":"dfc53f9f645435bcdb1a9d9f05a23b9fd9514872","tid":1223862,"uid":258927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:09:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/589475668207599620/589501460060831750/unknown.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F589475668207599620%2F589501460060831750%2Funknown.png&h=1434e808&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2821fc36c477aa95d6506774080553455d8dc47d","tid":1223862,"uid":258927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T20:25:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/589475668207599620/589550338701525002/unknown.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F589475668207599620%2F589550338701525002%2Funknown.png&h=6fbb1129&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}